reviewText:
Previous reviewer is correct.  Taylor does not wear blue jeans on stage and top is too trashy to be her.  Arms are too heavy to be Taylor.  Also, hair is completely wrong.

If you read the line at the bottom of cover "unauthorized"...no kinding!  scam alert!

i know for sure that Taylor Swift would not wear something like that on stage. Not only that, but the guitar is not her style, nor would her hair be that short and straight, and would not turn her back on the camera.
You need it to please females
Most of the DVD is videos I could have watched on YouTube and the narrator messed up a couple of times... I got it for cheap so I don't really mind.
My daughter loved getting this as she is a huge One Direction fan!  Anything that the boys are in is always a welcomed addition to her collection!
I would recommend this product. it was very nice and met all of my expectations. It came on time and I have no complaints!
My daughter loves it, it was for her birthday.  My daughter loves anything 1D! She had the best slumber party!
My DD liked it. she had seen the material before. She loves the boys so it was ok. Be aware your child my have already seen what is on this DVD.

Considering this is Unauthorized... no fan of Taylor Swift should put any money into such things.  The picture is not her on the cover, and in this case, I am judging by the cover.  Don't waste your money.

There is no way that's Taylor on the cover seeing as she doesn't own a guitar like that, and wouldn't play one on stage. That's not even her hair. If the cover isn't even right, I can hardly see how the information inside it can be.
and the person whos is taking a pic in the background is facing the other direction so the stage is o the other side
